            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>For high-stakes pages — homepage, pricing, and paid-ad landing pages — yes. A rewrite that lifts conversion by 20 to 40 percent typically pays for the copywriter within one month of traffic.</p></div></div>
